FBIS4-14630 "drsov064cc_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-064 Daily Report 4 Apr 1994 INTERREGIONAL AFFAIRS Baltic Legal Aid Agreement Comes Into Force 3 Apr Baltic Legal Aid Agreement Comes Into Force 3 Apr WS0404093994 Tallinn ETA in English 0710 GMT 4 Apr 94 WS0404093994 Tallinn ETA English BFN [From 4 April HOMMIKULEHT, p 3; "News Bulletin" No. 63/94] [Text] An agreement on legal aid and legal relations between the three Baltic states came into force on Sunday, April 3. The agreement guarantees the Baltic states citizens the right to appeal to the courts, prosecutors, notaries and other legal institutions of the three member countries. The agreement also concerns legal entities. The agreement was concluded on November 11, 1992 in Tallinn.
